		<p>Your privacy is important and we take it seriously. This Privacy Policy describes Menantang's policies and procedures on the collection, use and disclosure of your information when you use Menantang. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy. Swiss Federal Data Protection Law is applicable to all data made available to Menantang.</p>
		
		<h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>
		<p>Menantang uses information it collects to analyze how the Service is used, diagnose service or technical problems, maintain security, personalize content, remember information to help you efficiently access your account, monitor aggregate metrics such as total number of visitors, traffic, and demographic patterns, and track user content and users as necessary to comply with applicable laws. Menantang may collect the following types of information:</p>
		
